    "To compare these two strategies, we conduct experiments on the commonsense reasoning tasks following Hu et al. (2023).",
    "We first fine-tune LLaMA-3 8B model (AI@Meta, 2024) on 170k training samples (Hu et al., 2023), and then report the performance on 8 benchmarks, including ARCc/e (Clark et al., 2018), OBQA (Mihaylov et al., 2018), SIQA (Sap et al., 2019), WinoG.",
